        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop w-full max-w-3xl mt-12 md:mt-0">
            <h1 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md">

                Where will your next journey take you?

            </h1>
            <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-white/90 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto drop-shadow">
                Dünya'nın dört bir yanından gezginlerin ilham verici hikayelerini okuyarak gizli kalmış güzellikleri keşfedin, kendi maceranızı planlayın ve seyahat tutkunuzu paylaşın.
            </p>
            <!--Search / Filter Bar(Hero)-->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-full p-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto shadow-lg">
                <div class="flex-grow w-full md:w-auto relative flex items-center bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-3 md:py-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mr-3" data-icon="location_on"> location_on </span>
